# Systematic Alpha Research Lab — environment template
#
# The pipeline uses only free, public, keyless data sources by default
# (Yahoo Finance for ETF adjusted-close prices and macro series, FRED for CPI).
# No API key is required to reproduce the published research.
#
# The variables below are OPTIONAL. They let the price fetcher fall back to a
# keyed vendor if Yahoo Finance is ever rate-limited on your machine. If a key
# is absent, the fetcher uses Yahoo Finance and the cached raw responses.

# Tiingo daily adjusted-close API (https://www.tiingo.com) — optional fallback
TIINGO_API_TOKEN=

# Override the default download window if desired (ISO dates).
DATA_REQUESTED_START=2006-01-01
# DATA_REQUESTED_END defaults to the latest complete trading date.
DATA_REQUESTED_END=
